\begin_inset Formula $\int_{a}^{b} f(x) dx$
\end_inset

. Así : 
\begin_inset Formula \[
  \int_{a}^{b} f(x) dx  = \lim_{n \to \infty} \,
[f(x_1) + f(x_2) + \cdots + f(x_n) ]
 \,  \Delta x.
\]
